00:02.160 --> 00:04.400
<b>How many intruders, 
and where are they?</b>

00:04.400 --> 00:07.860
<b>From what I can detect, 
around eight of them.{he's using the wires from his imperial relic, but they haven't been brought up yet, so best to keep it vague like the jp}</b>

00:07.860 --> 00:10.360
<b>They're all in the vicinity of our base.</b>

00:10.360 --> 00:13.230
<b>I have to commend them 
for sniffing this place out.</b>

00:13.230 --> 00:15.200
<b>They're probably assassins 
from outside the empire.</b>

00:15.620 --> 00:18.410
<b>Move out. Let none escape.</b>

00:22.810 --> 00:25.200
