00:29.960 --> 00:31.220
<b>Right.</b>

00:31.220 --> 00:34.190
<b>Also, call me "Bro." 
Or "Handsome," if you prefer.</b>

00:34.190 --> 00:35.340
<b>Got it, Bro.</b>

00:35.340 --> 00:37.260
<b>All right! That's what I like to hear!</b>

00:37.260 --> 00:39.260
